{"tid":1009952,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"尼馬生日許願：想要新蹠骨","createTime":"2019-02-05T14:37:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-05T15:02:08.000Z","uid":153600,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"146bd622713aa1d845e3db2aa37966daa00cf127","tid":1009952,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T14:37:46.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=Hj%2FeMeEVpmzVIwD%2FtvFBFkkSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=a23a76a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】巴黎聖日耳門前鋒尼馬周二2月5日27歲生日，近年飽受傷患纏身的他，生日願望是希望有新的蹠骨！<br />\n<br />\n尼馬（Neymar）在周一舉辦了大型生日派對，跟200名親朋好友慶祝生日，正在療養右腳傷患的他撐著特製的紅色拐杖到場。<br />\n<br />\n壽星仔自然收到生日禮物，他表示：「我最想要的生日禮物是新的蹠骨，這樣我就可以在場上征戰，做我最愛的事，就是踢足球。」<br />\n<br />\n尼馬上月於法足盃傷出，右腳第5條蹠骨受創，需要休戰10個星期，肯定錯過歐聯16強兩鬥曼聯的大戰。事實上，他這個位置在去年2月已曾受創，當時嚴重得要提早收咧，幸好趕及在夏天世界盃傷癒復出。<br />\n<br />\n「終日都要用拐杖真的很難受，每位運動員都知道這苦處。隊友們給予我所有力量，爭取盡早復出。」尼馬續說。"},{"pid":"eae7022256e5319a1beaf5579237fe7904cd926f","tid":1009952,"uid":12628,"like":4,"dislike":7,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T14:45:07.000Z","msg":"成日比人踢一踢就碌成咁，難怪傷嘅<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/03/001202_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F03%2F001202_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=d4a5a354&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ac3214ee410de05cc471462d107d8872d745223f","tid":1009952,"uid":53773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eae7022256e5319a1beaf5579237fe7904cd926f","tid":1009952,"uid":12628,"like":4,"dislike":7,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T14:45:07.000Z","msg":"成日比人踢一踢就碌成咁，難怪傷嘅<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/03/001202_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F03%2F001202_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=d4a5a354&s={SIZE}